data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Charming updated home! Step into this move-in ready 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, with garage situated on large lot, and no HOA. Upon entering the front door be greeted by a spacious living room that effortlessly flows into the expansive open-concept living spaces. Natural light dances through the abundant windows, highlighting the graceful interplay of wood-look tile flooring, creating an inviting atmosphere that is both sophisticated and welcoming. The heart of the home resides in the open kitchen and adorned with decorative tile backsplash. The adjoining dining area is ideal for intimate family meals or gatherings. The primary suite exudes serenity and indulgence, featuring a private bathroom complete with walk-in shower. The additional well-appointed bedrooms offer ample space and comfort, catering to the needs of both family and guests. Take notice of the inside utility room that hosts extra flex space. Outside enjoy the fenced over-size backyard and create the perfect oasis as you see fit weather its hosting a barbecue, or simply relishing the tranquility of the environment! Immerse yourself in the coveted Winter Springs lifestyle, where modern luxury meets timeless elegance. Conveniently located, the property is close to a plethora of amenities, including schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation highways. Schedule a private showing today and discover the endless possibilities that await.
